   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Geschäft (Seelgerätstiftung) des Heinrich Payr</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> pr. mü., 2 Zg., Ma (Inde:x:: Item ain lateinischer brief dem abt von Schotten) <rs
                  type="event" ref="ev__StB_I_458">Venerabili in Christo patri ac domino domino
                  Scotorum abbati Wienne. Continua subiectio oracionum cum assiduitate indilate
                  precurrat. Domine ac pater honorabilis et discrete abbas Scotorum monasterii
                  ordinis sancti Benedicti. Auribus vestre pietatis presentibus visis instillare
                  nunc compellor, quod <rs type="fn" role="issuer">quidam <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__heinrich_payr_StB_I_458">excolonus Sancti Spiritus dictus Hainreich
                        Payr <roleName type="dead">obiit</roleName></rs></rs> in mea porrochia [!]
                  in Chawnperg, qui quidem <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org"
                        ref="org__wien-st_hieronymus-messe_payr_heinrich">pro perpetua
                        commemoracione anime sue testatus est ad Sanctum Jeronimum</rs></rs> hanc
                  vineam dictam Lampfleischprunn. <rs type="fn" role="witness">Huius spontanei
                     testamenti testes sunt <rs type="person" ref="pe__peter_StB_I_458"><roleName
                           type="title">dominus</roleName> Petrus <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="pe__heinrich_payr_StB_I_458">confessor eius</roleName></rs>, <rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__thomas_pistor_StB_I_458">Thomas <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Pistor</roleName>
                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__kaumberg"
                           ><add>ciues</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__niklas_carnifex_StB_I_458">Nicolaus <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Carnifex</roleName><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__kaumberg"><add>ciues</add></roleName></rs>, ciues predicti
                     opidi</rs>. Quapropter humiliter supplico ut hoc testamentum vestro adiutorio
                  confirmetur. Datum in die sanctorum Chrispini et Chrispiniani. <rs type="fn"
                     role="witness">Ex parte <rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_StB_I_458">Conradi
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__kaumberg-pfarre">plebani</roleName> in
                        Chawnperg</rs></rs>.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
